entries.journal_entry_description: You've started working for Borvo the Hutt on Naboo, the most notorious criminal on the planet.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Borvo's man Dagorel was shot in an ambush. Take him some medicine so he doesn't die in the swamps.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Go back and tell Borvo's guard that Dagorel got the medicine, and then that the two of you were jumped.
